ile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #103127<br />\n群龍共舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #51129<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分已加入編號，另外編號後面嘅括號代表別名或者舊名，有啲可能已經改咗名，大家要提防list入面嘅人，希望有更多巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為免有支那人混淆名單誤導大家，名單紀錄只以我「1000歳（人瑞）」為準<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/501799/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/501799/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"30bdee6c98ddcc1a0a88ef96b880ddcfddf5a06a","tid":516392,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多<br />\n支持去高登化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持迴聲室效應"},{"pid":"1a9b9460aeeb6bcd762444fca1c55a021e0549a7","tid":516392,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb8d5966ef9f7ee8bf72610d6218b41b8f5da9f4","tid":516392,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"777ee4525239d794df513186aaaf25aaf96693a0","tid":516392,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"絕對反對"},{"pid":"52d01903712b4629e14c379ea22cc50c1da38c92","tid":516392,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb8d5966ef9f7ee8bf72610d6218b41b8f5da9f4","tid":516392,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"真單機<br />\n等你解密得咁爽丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ed70133176bd9163af28c31a216acc153b01c0","tid":516392,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"22d5bec012d7f3c24871c18c1f0dade6f1e6cf7e","tid":516392,"uid":33481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"34ae9df7dd37014647d552d288e38d33f00c14f3","tid":516392,"uid":